tool_description: Quick & easy API to get the thumbnail of any YouTube Video & that too in multiple resolutions. Output: JSON Format or Direct JPEG.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://free-youtube-thumbnail.p.rapidapi.com/yt-thumbnails/index.php?"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "free-youtube-thumbnail.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
